quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  17,41,Futhi ngempela siziphindaphindile (izexwayiso) kuleQur’anukuze bakhumbuziseke futhi ayibanezeleli ngalutho ngaphandle kokwenqena
  17,42,"Ithi, “Ukube wayekanye nabanye onkulunkulu njengoba benza ngempela babezoyifuna indlela eya kumnikazi wesihlalo esiphakeme”"
  17,43,Udumo malube kuye! Futhi uphakeme ngaphezu kwalokho abakushoyo uphakeme kakhulu
  17,44,"Amazulu ayisikhombisa nomhlaba ayamdumisa kanye nanoma ngabe ubani, okuwona (amazulu ayisikhombisa nomhlaba uyamdumisa) futhi noma ngabe yintoni iyamdumisa ngodumo lwakhe kepha anikuqondi ukudumisa kwabo ngempela yena (uMvelinqangi) uyabekezela uyathethelela ngasosonke isikhathi"
  17,45,Futhi uma ufunda iQur’an sibeka isembozo esihlukanisayo phakathi kwakho kanye nalabo abangakholwa
  17,46,"Futhi sabeka izembozo ezinhliziyweni zabo, hleze bayiqonde futhi senza nezindlebe zabo ukuthi zingezwa futhi uma ukhumbule iNkosi yakho kwi-Qur’an (iNkosi) eyodwa vo bafulathelisa imihlane yabo bengathandi"
  17,47,"Thina siyakwazi ngokwedlulele lokho abakulalelayo uma bekulalela futhi uma benezingxoxo zangasese kulapho izoni zithi, “anilandeli muntu ngaphandle kwendoda elunjiwe”"
  17,48,Bheka ukuthi bakwenzela kanjani izibonelo kepha baduka ngakho-ke abazange bakwazi ukuthola indlela
  17,49,"Futhi bathi, “uma singamathambo siyizinhlayiya ezibuthuziwe ngakube ngempela siyovuswa sibe yizidalwa ezintsha na?”"
  17,50,"Ithi, “yibani ngamatshe noma nibe yinsimbi”"
  17,51,"Noma okunye kwezinye izinto ezidaliwe ezinkulu (ezibukhuni) ezifubeni zenu ngakho-ke bayothi, “ngubani oyosibuyisela emumva ekuphileni na? Ithi “yilowo owanidalayo ngesikhathi sokuqala” ngakho-ke bayonqankuzisela amakhanda abo kuwena bese bethi, “kuyokwenzeka nini lokho” ithi “Mhlawumbe kuseduzane”"
  17,52,Ngosuku lapho eyobe enimemeza bese niphendula ngendumiso yakhe futhi niyocabanga ukuthi anihlalanga ngaphandle kwesikhashana